```{r}
meteorites <- readr::read_csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/master/data/2019/2019-06-11/meteorites.csv")

str(meteorites)
summary(meteorites)
```

```{r}


name_types<-
  meteorites%>%
  group_by(y=as.factor(name_type))%>%
  select(y)%>%
  #distinct()%>%
  summarize(n=n())
  
 

```

```{r}

fall<-
  meteorites%>%
  group_by(y=as.factor(fall))%>%
  select(y)%>%
  #distinct()%>%
  summarize(n=n())
```

```{r}
year<-
  meteorites%>%
  drop_na()%>%
  group_by(y=as.factor(year))%>%
  select(y)%>%
  #distinct()%>%
  summarize(n=n())
```

```{r}
meteorites_2 <-
  
  meteorites%>%
  na.omit()
  filter(!is.na(year))
```

```{r}
meteorites_2<-
  na.omit(meteorites)
```
